:1},{"word":"last","count":1},{"word":"without","count":1},{"word":"question","count":1},{"word":"colosseum","count":1},{"word":"olymdos","count":1},{"word":"first","count":1},{"word":"ta-da","count":1},{"word":"village","count":1},{"word":"respite","count":1},{"word":"catch","count":1},{"word":"later","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"I... yes, of course!","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"Well, Champion, it's time to photograph the corruption of the Mournfell Canyon brought on by the Dark Tide. Next, we must stop by the <color=Highlight>Statue of Fabius the Hero</color>.","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"Wow, that's a brilliant shot, I bet you'd also be Champion in any photography contest!","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"See, that confidence would put anyone's doubts to rest. Let's head off now!","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"I can be your local guide and tell you all about the history of Septimont. I promise won't get bored on your journey.","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"Next stop, <color=Highlight>Border Mountains</color>!","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"What's the matter?","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"How did this little one end up lost here? I'll take it back home.","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"Champion, you'd know Common Echoes are treasured in Rinascita, but did you know that ever since gladiatorial combat became popular here, they've also become an irreplaceable part of Septimont's history?","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"Woe betide anyone who mistreats them. Anyway, help me snap a picture of Septimont City.","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"Our last stop without question is the <color=Highlight>Colosseum Olymdos</color>!","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"But first, I need to take Ta-da back to the Village of Respite. Catch you later!","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001}]}